{
  "stem": "4760.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then we had to go and take a shower.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then you had to go through a line where you would get your nice gray and blue uniform, the prisoner's uniform.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then you would go and get your number.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then you were put in barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And from there, they assigned you every day a different jobs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I had to go and work in the-- in the stone mill, clearing stones to be grinded, and-- and then other stones to be going into the camp to build streets, and stuff like that, in the-- in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, we were about three weeks, in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From Buchenwald, we then were-- were sent to-- did you want to ask something?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- yeah, we were separated from the Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Naturally, in Buchenwald, you had the barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were-- everybody had a certain barracks, a number assigned of barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were 100 barracks, and there were 100, 200 people in barracks-- 100, 150 people in barracks, because they had the bunk beds and all that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we were not really in touch with-- with the Jewish people, because they were, again, separate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we knew where they were, because of the stars, because they had the yellow star.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on the stars was written, Jude.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We-- we got the little red triangle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in the triangle, they would make an initial in it from which country you came from.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Like we came from France.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The people who came from Poland had a P in it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The people who came from-- from Czechoslovakia had a T in it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then the gypsy had the-- had-- had G in it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The-- and then they had the homosexuals.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They the pink ones-- triangle.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
